  <brief_title>Cognitive Dysfunction After Aneurysmal Subarachnoid Haemorrhage</brief_title>
  <official_title>Cognitive Dysfunction After Aneurysmal Subarachnoid Haemorrhage</official_title>
  <sponsors>
